metadata.name: Treat Your Pepe <3
metadata.description:
For the Pepe Fam & good friends of Pepe, who likes it shiny, brighty, lighty, like a diamondy!! 

It seems like this Rare Pepe having her best time at the Sparkling Pepe Nails Art Salon & Spa this afternoon. After a long week, let's chill and just treat yourself right! Which color looks good with that perfect green tan?! Oh, so many cool design options and time is a dime! 

At the Salon, we only have one motto! Repeat after me friends: Shine like gold, sparkle like glitter, don't forget to treat your inner frog much much better! 


5185 x 8000 px / 300 Dpi / .JPG 
Digitally Handmade Artwork 
by bluretina
